txt.en: 'If I owned the Pony, I'd hire this fellow to play in the common room every night!'
'Oh, he's quite good. I wish I had more time to stop and listen.'
'Oh. Thank you for the reminder! I will see you at the show tonight.'
'Well done, [placeholder]. I must see what else this show has to offer!'
'Ahh! A fireworks show does seem rather exciting! Thank you, friend.'
'Not bad. Not good.... but not bad.'
'It would have been better if you tuned up first.'
'That one was for you, my dear.'
'Here is another favourite of mine, I hope you enjoy it too.'
'A few more years and you'll make a passable bard, lad!'
'Address the low strings with more authority!'
